default              
defaultBreakthroughs in research 
defaultmay lead to expensive medicines coming to market. Action Duchenne is 
defaultseeking assurance that a 
default‘
defaultpostcode lottery
default’ for the funding of new drugs 
defaultwill not arise. Moreover, such drugs will have to administered and monitored by experts, therefore once again highlighting the need for regional expertise.
